OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772565069
OL,3,CCumbria Police to use facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology
OL,6,FCumbria Constabulary will use live
OL,7,Ffacial recognition (LFR) technology at
OL,8,Fan upcoming football match.
OL,10,FThe force will use LFR in the vicinity
OL,11,Fof Brunton Park at Carlisle United's
OL,12,Fgame against Southend United on
OL,13,FSaturday March 7, as part of an
OL,14,Foperation "designed to keep fans and
OL,15,Fthe public safe".
OL,17,FThe technology aims to identify people
OL,18,Fwanted for "serious offences" and
OL,19,Fthose subject to court orders,
OL,20,Faccording to Cumbria Police.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772565069
OL,3,CCumbria Police to use facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology
OL,6,FLive facial recognition will be
OL,7,Fdeployed alongside foot patrols and
OL,8,Fplain clothes officers.
OL,10,FDetective Superintendent Dan St
OL,11,FQuintin said: "LFR is an extra tool we
OL,12,Fcan deploy and use to help keep people
OL,13,Fsafe by specifically identifying
OL,14,Fpeople who are wanted by the police or
OL,15,Fwho are subject of a court order,
OL,16,Fincluding an order banning them from
OL,17,Fattending such an event.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772565069
OL,3,CCumbria Police to use facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology
OL,6,F"The cameras have been deployed at
OL,7,Fsimilar events in other parts of the
OL,8,Fcountry and will aid our efforts to
OL,9,Fhelp ensure that those attending the
OL,10,Ffixture can enjoy the game with their
OL,11,Ffamilies."
OL,13,FHow does live facial recognition work?
OL,15,FLive facial recognition compares faces
OL,16,Fcaptured by a camera feed against what
OL,17,FCumbria Police describes as a "secure,
OL,18,Fpredetermined watchlist made up of
OL,19,Findividuals wanted for serious
OL,20,Foffences, or who pose a risk to the
OL,21,Fpublic or themselves."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772565069
OL,3,CCumbria Police to use facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology
OL,6,FIf a match is identified, a police
OL,7,Fofficer will compare the image with
OL,8,Fthe person on camera, and determine
OL,9,Fwhether the match is accurate and
OL,10,Fwhether to speak to them. The
OL,11,Ftechnology will never determine this
OL,12,Falone, the constabulary promises.
OL,14,FWatchlist images are deleted after 24
OL,15,Fhours, while CCTV footage is deleted
OL,16,Fafter 31 days.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772565069
OL,3,CCumbria Police to use facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology
OL,6,FCumbria Police said: "If you are not
OL,7,Fon a watchlist, your biometric data is
OL,8,Fnever stored from passing through the
OL,9,FLFR zone of recognition. It is
OL,10,Fimmediately and automatically deleted,
OL,11,Fensuring privacy is protected."
OL,13,FCarlisle United Finance Director,
OL,14,FSuzanne Kidd, said: "Our focus at
OL,15,Fevery fixture at Brunton Park is to
OL,16,Fprovide a safe and welcoming
OL,17,Fenvironment for supporters, staff and
OL,18,Fthe wider community.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772565069
OL,3,CCumbria Police to use facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology
OL,6,F"We work closely with Cumbria Police
OL,7,Fand our partner agencies to ensure
OL,8,Fappropriate arrangements are in place,
OL,9,Fand we recognise the role that
OL,10,Fdevelopments in technology can play in
OL,11,Fsupporting that approach."
OL,13,FDet Supt St Quintin added: "With the
OL,14,F#10 ticket offer for the fixture,
OL,15,Fwe're expecting a large crowd for the
OL,16,Fmatch. This extra measure - put in
OL,17,Fplace in recognition of the larger
OL,18,Fthan usual crowd - will aid our
OL,19,Fofficers in ensuring everyone can
OL,20,Fenjoy the match safely.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
