FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1772565069
OL,3,CCumbria Police to use facial
OL,4,Crecognition technology
OL,6,F"We hope everyone attending enjoys the
OL,7,Fgame responsibly, whilst supporting
OL,8,Ftheir club."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/7
